shit makes me nostalgic and sad. i dont like feeling that way. stupid stupid old music that i use to listen to:

cruiserweight - first day of school ep - reminds me of my freshman summer and me and brittney went to local shows. goodtimes. mostly just the song trophy girl. haha
copeland - beneath the medicine tree - reminds me of when me and leana were all awesome and stuff. i miss it alot. the whole album.
co & ca - second stage turbine blade - i dont like it very much, but it reminds me of like christmas and stuff. fuck coheed. they suck.
hi-standard - growing up - reminds me of padre my freshman summer, because i listened to it on the way to padre, and on the way back. i <3 asian punk
the last chance diaries - your favorite expression - just because it made me all depressed last year and stuff. iunno
mewithoutyou - [a-->b] life - it reminds me of when i got mad, and id listen to that. its still good
punchline - rewind ep - just because. me and mike listened to it before baseball games and stuff, and when leana broke up with me i listened to it alot.
the rocket summer - this is me - i listened to that over summer when i was depressed, and it made me happy
the spill canvas - all hail the heartbreaker - iunno. i got that from amanda in humble, and it makes me miss summer. and its what me and amber fell asleep to.
the old 97's - question - from the night i slept over at leana's and i was like chris showed me them like a couple weeks ago. such a sweet song
saves the day - stay what you are - just about the whole album, because like iunno. nightingale was my song for leana when we were dating.
the get up kids -  anne arbour - had it when i was in middle school, and it makes me miss 8th grade and stuff. i had that song on every single mix cd i made back then.
straylight run - 6 song ep - leana. once again.
sparta - wiretap scars - it was good. and i always pretended like Jim was my uncle. haha. i was lame a couple summers ago
dashboard confessional - swiss army romance - yeah. you know why
new found glory - self titled - makes me miss austin, because i listened to that when i was going through the hill country right after i moved to houston.
weezer - the blue album - austin. dont mess with texas
weezer - the green album - i listened to that when i was going to splash town and junk. i miss season passes to splashtown.

i guess thats all. i was just listening to all my cd's and those ones got me all depressed and shit. im lame i know. but its an excuse to update. im bored, and i want quizno's. i ate tunafish for the first time in over a year today. it was good. i think im gonna go to quizno's. later taters.

well i am getting better... felicia and i talked for the first time in a month, because she toured asia... but she's back... and like after we got into the conversation... she's like... wow kyle, when i left you were a wreck, but you seem like your doing very well... and i guess i never noticed that i am doing better, and i guess it was like... whoa i am having progress, and i guess it was just good to hear from her after a whole month of no contact...

i also heard from meghan, and she said the same thing kinda... but she said im doing well too, and so those were like wake up calls... not really though, i just like talking to good friends that i havent talked to in a long time...

they both know im dying inside though, and so they didnt go into it with me, because the less i talk and think about it, the better i feel... so that was good...

and tomarrow me, brian, and darla are off work, so us and mike and chris are all gonna hang out all day... im excited, because i love those 4 and they are like my best distraction, so i should have a great day tomarrow...

well i guess im off... no one reads this... oh well

so im getting down on myself again... but im glad that i got my friends back... but yeah... im still not doing very well... i started smoking again, because it does get my mind off her...

this is so fucking strange... like ive been with 3 girls since her already, and but something always wants me to try and get her back, and so yeah i dunno...

i finally get shane... im pretty sure that he's doing what i did to lindsey... where he thinks that he likes her, and he convinces himself that too... and then he just gets tired of her and figures it out that, thats now how it is, and there are no feelings there... but he doesnt want to break her heart and tell her the truth, so he just leaves it alone, and just tries to be nice to her and stuff...

because it seems to me that lindsey is now going through the same thing that leana is going through... and i dunno... its just interesting... and but mike helps alot, and gets my mind off it.. thanks man... true best friend...

well thats all
